To investigate the correlation between TCID50 and the viral copy of RT-MRT-PCR, CSFV was diluted serially 10-fold and was assayed by RT-MRT-PCR. The R
2s of C-strain (genotype 1), Q90-278 (genotype 2), and 83-19 (genotype 3) strains between TCID50 and the viral copy were 0.998, 0.9082, 0.9741, respectively (Fig. 3
).
